  "name": "Power of the Marid",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/blue_25.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you gain the power of genies to grant wishes. Once per day, you can cast @Compendium[pf1.spells.s2p7a4biy7bl4ks2]{Limited Wish}&nbsp;as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Spell-Like-Abilities-Sp-\">spell-like ability</a>. Such wishes must begin with the words “I wish,” and cannot duplicate a @Compendium[pf1.spells.nnj51dwfkwd15ngj]{Wish}&nbsp;you have granted within the past 24 hours. If you use this ability to duplicate a spell with a costly material component, you must provide that component.</p>\n<p>You become immune to cold damage, and can use @Compendium[pf1.spells.q3st18udsalnyz5v]{Plane Shift}&nbsp;once per day to travel to or from the Plane of Water.</p>"
    },
